Class CreatePaloSearchFragment

  • java.lang.Object
    • androidx.fragment.app.Fragment
      • com.palo.palo.fragments.CreatePaloSearchFragment
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.view.View.OnCreateContextMenuListener, androidx.lifecycle.LifecycleOwner, androidx.lifecycle.ViewModelStoreOwner, androidx.savedstate.SavedStateRegistryOwner

    public class CreatePaloSearchFragment
extends androidx.fragment.app.Fragment
    This fragment is for creating a post. Allows users to search spotify to select an attachment for a post. This class is associated with fragment_create_palo_search.xml.
